#: .\books.json
msgid "Book of Ultimate Bashing"
msgid_plural "Books of Ultimate Bashing"
msgstr[0] "終極重擊之書"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Book of Ultimate Bashing', 'str_pl': 'Books of
#. Ultimate Bashing'}
#: .\books.json
msgid ""
"Oddly, this book is meant to whack things, rather than really teaching you "
"much. Although it is still a book, so don't expect it to last long."
msgstr "奇怪的是，這本書是用來敲打東西的，而不是真的教你什麼。不過它畢竟還是本書，所以別指望它能用很久。"

#: .\essencelike_items.json .\materials.json
msgid "Essence of Bashing"
msgid_plural "Essence of Bashings"
msgstr[0] "重擊精華"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Essence of Bashing'}
#: .\essencelike_items.json
msgid "Used to create items that are orientated around bashing."
msgstr "用於製作專注於重擊的物品。"

#: .\essencelike_items.json .\materials.json
msgid "Essence of Bacon"
msgid_plural "Essence of Bacons"
msgstr[0] "培根精華"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Essence of Bacon'}
#: .\essencelike_items.json
msgid "Used to create items that are orientated around bacon."
msgstr "用於製作專注於培根的物品。"

#: .\essencelike_items.json .\materials.json
msgid "Essence of Cutting"
msgid_plural "Essence of Cuttings"
msgstr[0] "切割精華"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Essence of Cutting'}
#: .\essencelike_items.json
msgid "Used to create items that are orientated around cutting."
msgstr "用於製作專注於切割的物品。"

#: .\essencelike_items.json
msgid "Plutonium Scale"
msgid_plural "Plutonium Scales"
msgstr[0] "鈈龍鱗片"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Plutonium Scale'}
#: .\essencelike_items.json
msgid ""
"A scale droppped from the LVL: 20 Plutonium Dragon! How the heck did you go "
"this? You cheated, didn't you?"
msgstr "從LVL: 20的鈈龍身上掉落的鱗片！你到底是怎麼做到的？你作弊了，對吧？"

#: .\essencelike_items.json .\materials.json
msgid "Shadow Bacon"
msgid_plural "Shadow Bacons"
msgstr[0] "暗影培根"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Shadow Bacon'}
#: .\essencelike_items.json
msgid ""
"This is no ordinary bacon, this is SHADOW bacon! A rare delicacy, almost "
"unheard of. It looks so amazing you feel unworthy being in it's presence, "
"much less eating it. So instead, you can honor this fabled bacon by turning "
"into freaking awesome gear! Either that or just sit it to collect dust on a "
"shelf in you bunker. That would work too."
msgstr ""
"這可不是普通的培根，這是暗影培根！一種罕見的珍饈，幾乎聞所未聞。它看起來如此驚豔，讓你覺得連站在它面前都不配，更別說吃掉了。所以，你可以通過把它變成超棒的裝備來向這傳說中的培根致敬！或者，你也可以把它放在掩體裡的架子上積灰。那樣也行。"

#: .\essencelike_items.json
msgid "Essence of Power"
msgid_plural "Essence of Powers"
msgstr[0] "力量精華"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Essence of Power'}
#: .\essencelike_items.json
msgid ""
"The ULTIMATE essence! Used to create by far the most powerful gear! You are "
"either a god or cheated by obtaining this legendary item!"
msgstr "終極精華！用於打造迄今為止最強大的裝備！你能得到這件傳奇物品，要麼是神，要麼就是作弊了！"

