#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Red's Odd Additions"
msgstr "Red的古怪附加內容"

#. ~ Description for Red's Odd Additions
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds some rather VERY OP items-test-stuff, odd creatures, and such to the "
"game. USE ONLY IF YOU ENJOY VERY OP ITEMS AND WACKINESS OR ONLY IF YOU ARE "
"TESTING"
msgstr "向遊戲中添加了一些相當非常OP的物品-測試-內容、古怪的生物等等。僅在您享受非常OP的物品和古怪樂趣時使用，或僅在測試時使用。"

#: .\creature\monster.json
msgid "tickle monster"
msgid_plural "tickle monsters"
msgstr[0] "撓癢怪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'tickle monster'}
#: .\creature\monster.json
msgid ""
"All this creature wants to do is tickle you! He's also very fast due to "
"being eternally fueled by caffeine, which tends to make it hard for you to "
"escape his soon-to-be-annoying tickles! He'll even do it in your sleep! What"
" a creep."
msgstr "這個生物只想撓你癢癢！它還非常快，因為它永遠被咖啡因驅動，這往往讓你很難逃脫它那即將變得煩人的撓癢！它甚至會在你睡覺時這麼做！真是個變態。"

#: .\gear\armor.json
msgid "Legendary Bacon Undies"
msgid_plural "Legendary Bacon Undiess"
msgstr[0] "傳奇培根內褲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Legendary Bacon Undies'}
#: .\gear\armor.json
msgid ""
"This is the fabled bacon undies of legend! You shall be IMMORTAL! Well, at "
"least to fire anyway. And have strangely deep pockets too!"
msgstr "這就是傳說中的傳奇培根內褲！你將變得不朽！嗯，至少對火來說是這樣。而且還有異常深的兜！"

#: .\gear\armor.json
msgid "Afro of Encumbrance"
msgid_plural "Afro of Encumbrances"
msgstr[0] "負累爆炸頭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Afro of Encumbrance'}
#: .\gear\armor.json
msgid ""
"Technically this is really just a wig. A very large wig at that. So much "
"that you can't wear anything else! On the bright side, it's so thick it's "
"like armor! Well, kinda."
msgstr "嚴格來說，這真的只是一頂假髮。而且是一頂非常大的假髮。大到你不能穿戴任何其他東西！不過好的一面是，它厚得像盔甲！嗯，差不多吧。"

#: .\gear\armor.json
msgid "Immortal Loincloth"
msgid_plural "Immortal Loincloths"
msgstr[0] "不朽纏腰布"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Immortal Loincloth'}
#: .\gear\armor.json
msgid ""
"No more will you need to worry about zombie hulks kicking you in the groin! "
"You won't feel a thing with this small item of clothing. Although it "
"protects literally nothing else."
msgstr "你再也不用擔心殭屍巨人踢你的襠部了！穿上這件小小的衣物，你什麼感覺都不會有。儘管它確實不保護任何其他部位。"

#: .\gear\armor.json
msgid "plutonium chestplate"
msgid_plural "plutonium chestplates"
msgstr[0] "鈈胸甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'plutonium chestplate'}
#: .\gear\armor.json
msgid ""
"It probably isn't very healthy to wear plutonium all day... But it looks "
"awesome! So who cares!?"
msgstr "整天佩戴鈈製品可能不太健康……但看起來超酷！誰在乎呢？"

#: .\gear\melee.json
msgid "Stick of Heroism"
msgid_plural "Stick of Heroisms"
msgstr[0] "英雄之杖"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Stick of Heroism'}
#: .\gear\melee.json
msgid ""
"Only to appear when the end of times come, this stick can only be held by a "
"true hero of the cataclysm!"
msgstr "唯有末日降臨之時才會現世，此杖僅能被真正的災變英雄所持握！"

#: .\gear\melee.json
msgid "serrated can"
msgid_plural "serrated cans"
msgstr[0] "鋸齒罐"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'serrated can'}
#: .\gear\melee.json
msgid ""
"You took a metal can and somehow serrated the sides of it. Be careful not to"
" lose a finger when using it."
msgstr "你拿了個金屬罐，還莫名其妙地把邊緣弄成了鋸齒狀。使用時當心別割傷手指。"

#: .\gear\melee.json
msgid "giant axe"
msgid_plural "giant axes"
msgstr[0] "巨型戰斧"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant axe'}
#: .\gear\melee.json
msgid ""
"Judging from the stupidly large weight and size, you can only assume this "
"was either used by a Transformer or some sort of gigantic monstrosity."
msgstr "從這蠢笨的巨大重量和尺寸來看，你只能推測它要麼是變形金剛用的，要麼屬於某種巨型怪物。"

#: .\gear\melee.json
msgid "plutonium dagger"
msgid_plural "plutonium daggers"
msgstr[0] "鈈制匕首"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'plutonium dagger'}
#: .\gear\melee.json
msgid "While small, this dagger can puncture through some serious armor!"
msgstr "這把匕首雖小，卻能刺穿某些重型護甲！"
